Hi [~dougt],

Providing reort logic, please use exact text Customer expects to see in the generated report. I.e. "ROI message" is not exact "ROI message" text-as-is. Current report version *doesn't* have any ROI logic so what "ROI message" should I display?

----

h3. *+Lets confirm "Homeless Risk Assessment Score" logic:*+
- if no assessment or no score, then text is "Undefined"
- if score < 15, then text is "Score does not meet minimum for group placement eligibility."
- if score >=15, then text is the exact score

*_Please confirm no changes should be done for "Homeless Risk Assessment Score".*_

----

h3. *+Current "Group Placement" text hierarchy:*+
1. age < 18 or health_dv_fleeing = 1, then text is {color:blue}"Client must have a signed release of information (ROI) on file to be placed in a group. If the client is fleeing domestic violence or is under age 18, they are not eligible for random assignment and should not sign the ROI."{color};
2. no assessment or no score, then text is {color:blue}"Client must complete the "Homeless Prevention Risk Tool" assessment for group placement."{color}
3. score > 14, then
- if client doesn't have Client Form, then text is {color:blue}"Client must have a signed Client Consent Form on file to be placed in a group."{color}
- if client has Client Form, then if c.id is odd, then text is {color:blue}"Group A - Financial Assistance"{color}, else text is {color:blue}"Group B - Case Management"{color}

----

h3. *+Expected "Group Placement" text hierarchy:*+
1. If client has no signed ROI *or* age < 18 *or* health_dv_fleeing = 1, then text is {color:blue}"Client must have a signed release of information (ROI) on file to be placed in a group. If the client is fleeing domestic violence or is under age 18, they are not eligible for random assignment and should not sign the ROI."{color}{color:green}please confirm/correct{color};
2. If client has a signed ROI and no Homeless Prevention Risk Tool, then text is {color:blue}"Client must complete the "Homeless Prevention Risk Tool" assessment for group placement."{color}{color:green}please confirm/correct{color};
3. If client has a signed ROI and Homeless Prevention Risk Tool and no Client Form, then text is {color:blue}"Client must have a signed Client Consent Form on file to be placed in a group."{color}{color:green}please confirm/correct{color};
4. If client has a signed ROI and Homeless Prevention Risk Tool and Client Form and ([score] <15 or [score]>29), then {color:green}what text should I display?{color}
5. If client has a signed ROI and Homeless Prevention Risk Tool and Client Form and [score] between 15 and 29, then if c.id is odd, then text is {color:blue}"Group A - Financial Assistance"{color}, else text is {color:blue}"Group B - Case Management"{color}

*Extimate: 1 hour* (30 min out of 1 hour is for writing this comment :))

Best regards,
Natalie

